6 "23-5-702. Casino nights night and expanded casino night authorized -- allowed activities --
7 limit. (1) (a) Nonprofit organizations Subject to subsection (2), a nonprofit organization may conduct or
8 participate in a casino night.
9 (b) The following gambling activities may be conducted during a casino night:
10 (i) live card games authorized under 23-5-311;
11 (ii) live bingo and keno games; and
12 (iii) raffles.
13 (2) (a) A nonprofit organization may conduct or participate in an expanded casino night a
14 maximum of once a year.
