16 (i) live card games authorized under 23-5-311;
17 (ii) live blackjack, twenty-one, jacks or better, baccarat, or chemin de fer;
18 (iii) live bingo and keno games;
19 (iv) raffles;
20 (v) roulette, including the use of a roulette wheel;
21 (vi) dice games known as craps, hazard, or chuck-a luck, including a craps table; and
22 (vii) box faro, including the use of a faro box or faro layout."
